title: PixelFlash USB 3.0 No-Bend Pins Compact Flash Memory Card Reader SuperSpeed CF Adapter (PFUSB3CFRD)
description: Pixel Flash CF readers are specifically designed to stop the dreaded "bent pin syndrome" that all the value priced CF readers suffer from. That means these bad boys work when you need them without requiring a soft touch. On top of that, you've made the investment in high speed CF cards, so you need a USB 3.0 Card Reader to match. With read speeds up to 500 MB/s and transfers up to a smoldering 5GB/s, you can move your images and video in a fraction of the time. Our small, rugged and rubberized CF readers are ready for the rigors of the field and handsome enough to inspire a bit of friendly rivalry at the office. So let's get to work, let's spend less time staring at a progress bar and more time shooting, and let's not fuss over busted gear, our pins won't bend or break.
